<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Hifz Management | Imam Gazzali Academy</title>
    <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Plus+Jakarta+Sans:wght@400;500;600;700;800&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
     <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/hifz-management.css">
</head>
<body>

    <div class="bg-orb orb-1"></div>
    <div class="bg-orb orb-2"></div>

    <main class="dashboard-wrapper">
        <a href="/dashboard" class="btn-back">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><line x1="19" y1="12" x2="5" y2="12"></line><polyline points="12 19 5 12 12 5"></polyline></svg>
            Back to Dashboard
        </a>

        <header>
            <h1 class="page-title">Hifz Management</h1>
            <p class="page-subtitle">Track and manage memorization progress efficiently across all levels of the academy with professional precision.</p>
        </header>

        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
            
            <div class="glass-card stagger-1">
                <div class="icon-box">
                    <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M12 20v-6M6 20V10M18 20V4"></path></svg>
                </div>
                <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3">Progress Tracking</h3>
                <p class="text-slate-500 mb-8 leading-relaxed">View and manage Hifz students' memorization progress including Padam, Sabk Juz, and Murajah.</p>
                <a href="/hifz/progress" class="btn-primary">
                    View Hifz Students
                    <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><line x1="5" y1="12" x2="19" y2="12"></line><polyline points="12 5 19 12 12 19"></polyline></svg>
                </a>
            </div>

             <div class="glass-card stagger-2">
                <div class="icon-box">
                    <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M12 20v-6M6 20V10M18 20V4"></path></svg>
                </div>
                <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3">Usthad Management</h3>
                <p class="text-slate-500 mb-8 leading-relaxed">Manage and organize usthads efficiently by assigning them to classes and maintaining their access within the system.</p>
                <a href="/hifz/usthads" class="btn-primary">
                    Manage Usthads
                    <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><line x1="5" y1="12" x2="19" y2="12"></line><polyline points="12 5 19 12 12 19"></polyline></svg>
                </a>
            </div>

            <div class="glass-card stagger-2">
                <div class="icon-box">
                    <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M12 20v-6M6 20V10M18 20V4"></path></svg>
                </div>
                <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3">Class Management</h3>
                <p class="text-slate-500 mb-8 leading-relaxed">Manage Class</p>
                <a href="/hifz/classes" class="btn-primary">
                    Manage Classes
                    <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><line x1="5" y1="12" x2="19" y2="12"></line><polyline points="12 5 19 12 12 19"></polyline></svg>
                </a>
            </div>
            
            <div class="glass-card stagger-3">
                <div class="icon-box">
                    <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M16 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-4-4H6a4 4 0 0 0-4 4v2"></path><circle cx="9" cy="7" r="4"></circle><path d="M22 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-3-3.87"></path><path d="M16 3.13a4 4 0 0 1 0 7.75"></path></svg>
                </div>
                <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3">Attendance</h3>
                <p class="text-slate-500 mb-8 leading-relaxed">Track daily attendance and maintain historical records for every Hifz student automatically.</p>
                <button class="btn-primary btn-disabled">Coming Soon</button>
            </div>

            <div class="glass-card stagger-4">
                <div class="icon-box">
                    <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M14 2H6a2 2 0 0 0-2 2v16a2 2 0 0 0 2 2h12a2 2 0 0 0 2-2V8z"></path><polyline points="14 2 14 8 20 8"></polyline><line x1="16" y1="13" x2="8" y2="13"></line><line x1="16" y1="17" x2="8" y2="17"></line></svg>
                </div>
                <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3">Reports</h3>
                <p class="text-slate-500 mb-8 leading-relaxed">Generate and view structured reports of student progress, performance metrics, and insights.</p>
                <button class="btn-primary btn-disabled">Coming Soon</button>
            </div>

        </div>

        <footer class="mt-16 pt-8 border-t border-slate-200/50 text-center text-slate-400 text-sm font-semibold stagger-3">
            &copy; 2026 Imam Gazzali Academy • Professional Management Suite
        </footer>
    </main>
</body>
</html>  